name: BoA Custom Gift Wrapping
description:
Have Built of America gift wrap your purchase for a special someone or your special self.

We use USA recycled craft paper tied with twine. Built of America gift wrap looks impeccable and unwraps with ease. 

A handstamped card is included with each gift wrap purchase. Contact Built of America to have us handwrite a custom message on the card. 

Please contact Built of America if your purchase includes multiple items to clarify the item to gift wrap.

name: 1 Color Black Printer  – Limited Edition Screenprint
description:
Limited Edition Screenprint
*All Prints are printed on American-made heavy stock French Paper Co. paper.


Description:
1 Color Black Printer is the result of one image rapidly found through the American Internet.  The image is arranged and outlined by hand to produce 1 Color Black Printer.  The final image is hand-printed onto high-quality domestic paper.

Your Built of America print can reside gracefully in any frame from the über-minimalist to the ultra-ornate to coordinate seamlessly with your decor.  Matting the image is suggested as it allows you to crop the white space according to your framing needs.  


Process:
Original one-color offset experimental screen print. The screen is prepared with a mixture of shellac-based ink and screen printing medium and pressed once.  The print is offset slightly and pressed again with the same color. The resulting prints are highly non-traditional, unique and beautiful compared to other screen prints.

This printing process is highly unique and each edition is limited. The process will not be repeated for this image. Once stock sells out, there will be no second edition printed. 

Edition of 5. 

Dimensions:  12.5”W X 19”L

Disclaimer: Built of America limited edition prints may vary in character. The print pictured above may not be exactly what you are getting.  In certain editions the prints vary wildly.  If this is a concern please contact us BEFORE placing your order.

Please feel free to inquire about specifics.

name: Face of – Limited Edition Monoprint
description:
Limited Edition Monoprint - Internet series
*All Prints are printed on American made heavy stock French Paper Co. paper.


Description:
Face of is the result of several images rapidly found through the American Internet.  The image is arranged and outlined by hand to produce Face of. The final image is hand-printed onto high-quality domestic paper.

Your Built of America print can reside gracefully in any frame from the über-minimalist to the ultra-ornate to coordinate seamlessly with your decor.  Matting the image is suggested as it allows you to crop the white space according to your framing needs. 

Process:
Original one-of-a-kind experimental inkjet transfer print. The heavy stock paper is prepared in a mixture of water and alcohol. The ink is digitally rendered on acetate and pressed wet onto the soaked paper by a hand-rolling process. These are NOT giclée, cut or screen-printed. The resulting prints are highly non-traditional, unique and beautiful works of art, each displaying its own unique characteristics.

name: Passive Amplifier for iPhone - Rare Hardwood Maple
description:
Limited Edition Passive Amplifier for iPhone.


Rare Hardwood Maple grown in Vermont. 

All Amps in this edition are made from Maple featuring special alignments. Each piece includes at least one and up to three of the following: Bird’s Eye, Tiger, Curly. 

This edition of three Amps is made from rare hardwood Maple from a small-scale supplier in Vermont. 

All Amps in this edition are handmade and numbered by the craftsperson.

Each Amplifier is from a specific edition with the information labeled on the bottom.
Each Amplifier is made by hand by one person without measurements. The only sure measurement is the hole for the iPhone itself. Therefore each Amp will be slightly different in size and character. 

Each Amplifier makes use of the acoustics of the wood and the mono speaker of the iPhone to amplify the built-in sound up to a 10dB increase. The sound takes on an extra degree of warmth from the wood itself and makes for a purely enjoyable listening experience. When the built-in iPhone speaker won’t cut it, our Amp is the perfect solution. No cords or batteries to contend with. 

Looks great with most decor. The finish is a light danish oil stain combined with some shellac to give it a durable and warm finish. The grain and characteristics of the wood are different for each Amp so please keep in mind that what’s pictured above may not match exactly what you receive.

Approximate measurements: 2.5"H X 4"D X 6"L

All wood is purchased locally in Vermont from various avenues.

This is a limited edition set. Any set made after this set is sold out will be of the same principle but noticeably different in character.

Please feel free to inquire about specifics.
